title: Wildcats injury report for Colorado
text:
Wildcats injury report for Colorado Posted: TUCSON, AZ (Arizona Athletics) - 
The following is the Arizona Wildcats injury report heading into Saturday’s game at Colorado. WR Trey Griffey, who hasn't played this season because of foot injury, upgraded to probable for Saturday at Colorado. #ArizonaWildcats — Anthony Gimino (@AGWildcatReport) October 15, 2015 
Probable LB Haden Gregory (knee) #ArizonaWildcats injury report lists three as questionable: CB DaVonte' Neal (hammy), DL Jeff Worthy (concussion), RB Nick Wilson (foot). — Anthony Gimino (@AGWildcatReport) October 15, 2015 
Questionable
